<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Mari Chan Pha</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. I damlai ni hawu hi sawtta puona,
 A liem zing nicheng leh zan chengin;
 Ka Lalpa dinga hun chu mang loin,
 Dan leh ti'n hun tam a liem mang zotai.

[V2]
 Malai Martha'n a buoipih chu.
 Hukdampa'n kipahpih lo;
 Mari'n chanpha ana tel hi,
 :Sukbuoi ding ei puoi&quot; tin a hilh;
 Mari chanpha chu na chang kha ngei tam?

[V3]
 2. I damsung lungkham buoinate haw hi,
 A mangthai zing a nawpnate tawh;
 Kumsawt gam tungzo ding him a um puou,
 Kumsawta um ding ka Lal na lo chu.

[V4]
 3. Van Kanaan gam hawih chu I zawt lai un,
 Lungkham buoina te'n ei tuom vel a;
 I damsung lungkham buoinate haw hi,
 Paih in Mari chan pha chu chang hitiu.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>324</hymn_number>
</song>